{"tid":1174921,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【人體運毒致死】日男吞246包可卡因運毒 墨西哥飛東京期間抽搐暴斃","createTime":"2019-05-28T07:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-28T08:36:12.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4dd8ecc6dc7e896b993d41273d6abf33bb55e7fa","tid":1174921,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T07:59:12.000Z","msg":"一名日本男子在哥倫比亞首都波哥大飛往日本東京途中暴斃，他搭乘的班機在墨西哥北部緊急降落，當局在他體內發現246包可卡因。<br />\n墨西哥索諾拉州（Sonora）檢察署表示，42歲死者由波哥大飛到墨西哥市，再轉機飛往日本，但他轉機由墨西哥市飛往東京期間，在航程不久開始抽搐，空中服務員發現後，隨即請求緊急降落索諾拉州艾莫西約（Hermosillo）。<br />\n聲明指出，飛機在24日清晨2時25分降落，醫護人員登機後宣佈男子不治。聲明未透露男子姓名，僅以有津（Udo N）稱呼他。驗屍發現這名男子吞下246包、每包長2.5厘米闊1厘米的可卡因，死因是藥物過量引發腦水腫。以人體運毒是販毒集團常用的走私手法。<br />\n涉事班機由墨西哥國際航空公司（Aeromexico）營運，當時機上還載有198名乘客，男子遺體移下機後，飛機繼續航程。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190528/large/1559012971_e909.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190528%2Flarge%2F1559012971_e909.jpg&h=340cc2ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190528/59648975\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F59648975&d=4a077UaaKOqSfaiyS2iiQVpzQI%2FFghXCkDWT3grjsfs%3D&h=e3250401\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190528%2F59648975&h=827a26dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20190528/59648975</a>"},{"pid":"5234246a419ad0a7f914708004b66590c9a55785","tid":1174921,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:01:17.000Z","msg":"點撚樣吞246包可卡因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd582d7216551bdefa366062aea0e52b572bf08","tid":1174921,"uid":51701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:03:57.000Z","msg":"一定係大陸人扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6245c77869f5a21eb48325ecdc82bc42ede63b9e","tid":1174921,"uid":1374,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:05:45.000Z","msg":"Lucy<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0304ac240cec52b05a607b24d3576a3c7d4a1d8b","tid":1174921,"uid":44638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"啪一包都死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e21c9b7741a0fce153218c76f410588ded61a70","tid":1174921,"uid":173179,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5234246a419ad0a7f914708004b66590c9a55785","tid":1174921,"uid":160662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:01:17.000Z","msg":"點撚樣吞246包可卡因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:32:49.000Z","msg":"唔記得邊套戲話加d牛油就吞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e740fcb736fc46d32b673cfe85dc7c3beb33dea","tid":1174921,"uid":63950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:33:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e12876d5fc9dc685c12d85b945e9439bc852431f","tid":1174921,"uid":253954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:35:53.000Z","msg":"不如好似lucy咁切開個肚藏毒好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c47630e90902b1d2baf0d77937e1170529bdf2af","tid":1174921,"uid":75448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-28T08:36:12.000Z","msg":"係體內爆左包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/